{"id": "figure_002", "modality": "figures", "name": "ResNet Bottleneck Residual Block", "task": {"description": "Create a single 1920x1080 self-contained HTML file using ONLY inline CSS and inline SVG that reproduces a ResNet bottleneck residual block figure. Title 'ResNet Bottleneck Block' at top in 32px bold. A vertical main path of three convolution boxes in sequence, bottom to top: '1x1 conv, 64' (reduce), '3x3 conv, 64', '1x1 conv, 256' (expand), each followed by 'BN + ReLU' annotations. Below the stack an input tensor annotation 'x: 256-d', above the stack the output. To the RIGHT of the main path draw a curved identity skip-connection arrow that bypasses all three conv boxes and rejoins at a circular '+' (element-wise addition) node above the last conv, followed by a final 'ReLU' box. Label the skip arrow 'identity'. Show channel-count annotations (64, 64, 256) on each conv box and the bottleneck reduction ratio. The skip path must NOT pass through any conv box. Center the whole block. HARDEN (density + alignment): ALSO include (a) a LEGEND box that maps every distinct block color and every arrow/line style used in the figure, and (b) a small tensor-shape annotation on each major block (e.g. 'BxNxd'). Pack the figure densely with at least 14 labeled elements; every group of sibling blocks must be equal-size and share edges, with uniform gutters, and nothing may overlap or clip.", "requirements": ["All boxes (three conv boxes, the '+' addition node, the final ReLU box, input and output annotations) are visible within the 1920x1080 viewport with no clipping at any edge", "No two boxes overlap each other", "Every box label text is fully contained inside its rectangle with no overflow", "The identity skip-connection arrow bypasses all three conv boxes and does not pass through any of them", "The skip arrow terminates at the circular '+' addition node and the '+' node sits above the third conv and below the final ReLU", "Channel-count annotations '64', '64', and '256' each appear on the correct conv box and are legible", "The 'identity' label on the skip arrow does not overlap any box or other text", "The three conv boxes have equal vertical gaps between them (even spacing)", "No element is within 10px of any viewport edge", "No horizontal or vertical scrollbar appears; all content fits inside 1920x1080", "A legend box maps every block color and arrow/line style used; each major block carries a tensor-shape annotation; sibling blocks are equal-size and edge-aligned with uniform gutters; no element overlaps or is clipped"]}, "runs": [{"run": 1, "ss_n_defects": 0, "ss_text_overlap": 0, "ss_clipped": 0, "ss_overflow": 0, "ss_total_tokens": 4327, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": 0, "rv_clipped": 0, "rv_overflow": 0, "rv_iterations": 1, "rv_total_tokens": 4493}, {"run": 2, "ss_n_defects": 0, "ss_text_overlap": 0, "ss_clipped": 0, "ss_overflow": 0, "ss_total_tokens": 4263, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": 0, "rv_clipped": 0, "rv_overflow": 0, "rv_iterations": 1, "rv_total_tokens": 4487}, {"run": 3, "ss_n_defects": 0, "ss_text_overlap": 0, "ss_clipped": 0, "ss_overflow": 0, "ss_total_tokens": 4318, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": 0, "rv_clipped": 0, "rv_overflow": 0, "rv_iterations": 1, "rv_total_tokens": 4284}], "ss_img": "images/figures/figure_002_ss.jpg", "rv_img": "images/figures/figure_002_rv.jpg", "ss_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>ResNet Bottleneck Block</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            width: 1920px;\n            height: 1080px;\n            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n            background: #f8f9fa;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        \n        .container {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n        }\n        \n        .title {\n            font-size: 32px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: #2c3e50;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"title\">ResNet Bottleneck Block</div>\n        \n        <svg width=\"1600\" height=\"900\" viewBox=\"0 0 1600 900\">\n            <!-- Main Path Convolution Blocks -->\n            <!-- 1x1 conv, 64 (reduce) -->\n            <rect x=\"400\" y=\"650\" width=\"200\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#3498db\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"500\" y=\"680\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\">1\u00d71 conv, 64</text>\n            <text x=\"500\" y=\"700\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\">(reduce)</text>\n            <text x=\"500\" y=\"720\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"10\">B\u00d7H\u00d7W\u00d764</text>\n            \n            <!-- BN + ReLU for first conv -->\n            <rect x=\"420\" y=\"540\" width=\"160\" height=\"40\" fill=\"#e74c3c\" stroke=\"#c0392b\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"6\"/>\n            <text x=\"500\" y=\"565\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\">BN + ReLU</text>\n            \n            <!-- 3x3 conv, 64 -->\n            <rect x=\"400\" y=\"430\" width=\"200\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#3498db\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"500\" y=\"460\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\">3\u00d73 conv, 64</text>\n            <text x=\"500\" y=\"480\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\">(bottleneck)</text>\n            <text x=\"500\" y=\"500\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"10\">B\u00d7H\u00d7W\u00d764</text>\n            \n            <!-- BN + ReLU for second conv -->\n            <rect x=\"420\" y=\"320\" width=\"160\" height=\"40\" fill=\"#e74c3c\" stroke=\"#c0392b\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"6\"/>\n            <text x=\"500\" y=\"345\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\">BN + ReLU</text>\n            \n            <!-- 1x1 conv, 256 (expand) -->\n            <rect x=\"400\" y=\"210\" width=\"200\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#3498db\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"500\" y=\"240\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\">1\u00d71 conv, 256</text>\n            <text x=\"500\" y=\"260\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\">(expand)</text>\n            <text x=\"500\" y=\"280\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"10\">B\u00d7H\u00d7W\u00d7256</text>\n            \n            <!-- Input tensor annotation -->\n            <rect x=\"350\" y=\"760\" width=\"300\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#95a5a6\" stroke=\"#7f8c8d\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"6\"/>\n            <text x=\"500\" y=\"790\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\">x: 256-d input</text>\n            <text x=\"500\" y=\"805\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"10\">B\u00d7H\u00d7W\u00d7256</text>\n            \n            <!-- Element-wise addition node -->\n            <circle cx=\"500\" cy=\"140\" r=\"25\" fill=\"#f39c12\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"3\"/>\n            <text x=\"500\" y=\"148\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"20\" font-weight=\"bold\">+</text>\n            \n            <!-- Final ReLU -->\n            <rect x=\"420\" y=\"60\" width=\"160\" height=\"40\" fill=\"#e74c3c\" stroke=\"#c0392b\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"6\"/>\n            <text x=\"500\" y=\"85\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\">ReLU</text>\n            \n            <!-- Output annotation -->\n            <rect x=\"350\" y=\"10\" width=\"300\" height=\"40\" fill=\"#27ae60\" stroke=\"#229954\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"6\"/>\n            <text x=\"500\" y=\"35\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\">Output: B\u00d7H\u00d7W\u00d7256</text>\n            \n            <!-- Main path arrows -->\n            <path d=\"M 500 760 L 500 730\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <path d=\"M 500 650 L 500 580\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <path d=\"M 500 540 L 500 510\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <path d=\"M 500 430 L 500 360\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <path d=\"M 500 320 L 500 290\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <path d=\"M 500 210 L 500 165\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <path d=\"M 500 115 L 500 100\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Skip connection (identity) - curved path -->\n            <path d=\"M 650 785 Q 750 450 650 140\" stroke=\"#9b59b6\" stroke-width=\"4\" fill=\"none\" stroke-dasharray=\"8,4\" marker-end=\"url(#skipArrow)\"/>\n            <text x=\"720\" y=\"460\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#9b59b6\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\">identity</text>\n            <text x=\"720\" y=\"480\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#9b59b6\" font-size=\"10\">skip connection</text>\n            \n            <!-- Channel annotations -->\n            <text x=\"320\" y=\"695\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\">256\u219264</text>\n            <text x=\"320\" y=\"475\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\">64\u219264</text>\n            <text x=\"320\" y=\"255\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\">64\u2192256</text>\n            \n            <!-- Bottleneck ratio annotation -->\n            <rect x=\"50\" y=\"400\" width=\"180\" height=\"120\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"140\" y=\"425\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\">Bottleneck Ratio</text>\n            <text x=\"140\" y=\"445\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"12\">256 \u2192 64 \u2192 256</text>\n            <text x=\"140\" y=\"465\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"12\">Reduction: 4\u00d7</text>\n            <text x=\"140\" y=\"485\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"12\">Parameters: \u219375%</text>\n            <text x=\"140\" y=\"505\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"12\">Computation: \u219350%</text>\n            \n            <!-- Legend -->\n            <rect x=\"1200\" y=\"150\" width=\"350\" height=\"400\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"1375\" y=\"180\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\">Legend</text>\n            \n            <!-- Legend items -->\n            <rect x=\"1220\" y=\"200\" width=\"40\" height=\"25\" fill=\"#3498db\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"1\" rx=\"4\"/>\n            <text x=\"1275\" y=\"218\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"12\">Convolution Layer</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"1220\" y=\"235\" width=\"40\" height=\"20\" fill=\"#e74c3c\" stroke=\"#c0392b\" stroke-width=\"1\" rx=\"4\"/>\n            <text x=\"1275\" y=\"248\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"12\">Batch Norm + ReLU</text>\n            \n            <circle cx=\"1240\" cy=\"275\" r=\"12\" fill=\"#f39c12\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"1275\" y=\"280\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"12\">Element-wise Addition</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"1220\" y=\"295\" width=\"40\" height=\"20\" fill=\"#95a5a6\" stroke=\"#7f8c8d\" stroke-width=\"1\" rx=\"4\"/>\n            <text x=\"1275\" y=\"308\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"12\">Input Tensor</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"1220\" y=\"325\" width=\"40\" height=\"20\" fill=\"#27ae60\" stroke=\"#229954\" stroke-width=\"1\" rx=\"4\"/>\n            <text x=\"1275\" y=\"338\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"12\">Output Tensor</text>\n            \n            <line x1=\"1220\" y1=\"355\" x2=\"1260\" y2=\"355\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\"/>\n            <text x=\"1275\" y=\"360\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"12\">Main Path Flow</text>\n            \n            <line x1=\"1220\" y1=\"380\" x2=\"1260\" y2=\"380\" stroke=\"#9b59b6\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-dasharray=\"6,3\"/>\n            <text x=\"1275\" y=\"385\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"12\">Skip Connection</text>\n            \n            <text x=\"1230\" y=\"410\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"11\">B: Batch size</text>\n            <text x=\"1230\" y=\"425\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"11\">H\u00d7W: Spatial dimensions</text>\n            <text x=\"1230\" y=\"440\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"11\">d: Channel depth</text>\n            \n            <text x=\"1375\" y=\"470\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\">ResNet-50 Architecture</text>\n            <text x=\"1375\" y=\"490\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"11\">Bottleneck design reduces</text>\n            <text x=\"1375\" y=\"505\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"11\">computational complexity</text>\n            <text x=\"1375\" y=\"520\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"11\">while maintaining accuracy</text>\n            \n            <!-- Arrow markers -->\n            <defs>\n                <marker id=\"arrowhead\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                    <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n                </marker>\n                <marker id=\"skipArrow\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                    <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#9b59b6\"/>\n                </marker>\n            </defs>\n        </svg>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>", "rv_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>ResNet Bottleneck Block</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            width: 1920px;\n            height: 1080px;\n            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n            background: #f8f9fa;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        \n        .container {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: flex-start;\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n        \n        .title {\n            font-size: 32px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: #2c3e50;\n            margin-bottom: 60px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"title\">ResNet Bottleneck Block</div>\n        \n        <svg width=\"1840\" height=\"900\" viewBox=\"0 0 1840 900\">\n            <!-- Main convolution path -->\n            <!-- Input tensor -->\n            <rect x=\"400\" y=\"750\" width=\"120\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#e8f4fd\" stroke=\"#3498db\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n            <text x=\"460\" y=\"775\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Input</text>\n            <text x=\"460\" y=\"795\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#34495e\">x: 256-d</text>\n            \n            <!-- 1x1 conv reduce -->\n            <rect x=\"400\" y=\"620\" width=\"120\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#fff2e6\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n            <text x=\"460\" y=\"645\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">1\u00d71 conv</text>\n            <text x=\"460\" y=\"665\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#34495e\">64 filters</text>\n            <text x=\"460\" y=\"685\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">BxHxW\u00d764</text>\n            \n            <!-- BN + ReLU for 1x1 conv -->\n            <rect x=\"540\" y=\"635\" width=\"80\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#f0f8e6\" stroke=\"#27ae60\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"3\"/>\n            <text x=\"580\" y=\"655\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">BN</text>\n            <text x=\"580\" y=\"670\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">ReLU</text>\n            \n            <!-- 3x3 conv -->\n            <rect x=\"400\" y=\"480\" width=\"120\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#fff2e6\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n            <text x=\"460\" y=\"505\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">3\u00d73 conv</text>\n            <text x=\"460\" y=\"525\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#34495e\">64 filters</text>\n            <text x=\"460\" y=\"545\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">BxHxW\u00d764</text>\n            \n            <!-- BN + ReLU for 3x3 conv -->\n            <rect x=\"540\" y=\"495\" width=\"80\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#f0f8e6\" stroke=\"#27ae60\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"3\"/>\n            <text x=\"580\" y=\"515\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">BN</text>\n            <text x=\"580\" y=\"530\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">ReLU</text>\n            \n            <!-- 1x1 conv expand -->\n            <rect x=\"400\" y=\"340\" width=\"120\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#fff2e6\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n            <text x=\"460\" y=\"365\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">1\u00d71 conv</text>\n            <text x=\"460\" y=\"385\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#34495e\">256 filters</text>\n            <text x=\"460\" y=\"405\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">BxHxW\u00d7256</text>\n            \n            <!-- BN for final conv -->\n            <rect x=\"540\" y=\"355\" width=\"80\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#f0f8e6\" stroke=\"#27ae60\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"3\"/>\n            <text x=\"580\" y=\"375\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">BN</text>\n            <text x=\"580\" y=\"390\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">(no ReLU)</text>\n            \n            <!-- Element-wise addition -->\n            <circle cx=\"460\" cy=\"250\" r=\"25\" fill=\"#ffeaa7\" stroke=\"#fdcb6e\" stroke-width=\"3\"/>\n            <text x=\"460\" y=\"258\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"20\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">+</text>\n            \n            <!-- Final ReLU -->\n            <rect x=\"420\" y=\"160\" width=\"80\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#f0f8e6\" stroke=\"#27ae60\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"3\"/>\n            <text x=\"460\" y=\"180\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">ReLU</text>\n            <text x=\"460\" y=\"195\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">BxHxW\u00d7256</text>\n            \n            <!-- Output tensor -->\n            <rect x=\"400\" y=\"80\" width=\"120\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#e8f4fd\" stroke=\"#3498db\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n            <text x=\"460\" y=\"105\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Output</text>\n            <text x=\"460\" y=\"125\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#34495e\">256-d</text>\n            \n            <!-- Skip connection path -->\n            <path d=\"M 600 780 Q 750 780 750 520 Q 750 260 600 250\" \n                  fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#9b59b6\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-dasharray=\"8,4\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Skip connection label -->\n            <text x=\"750\" y=\"520\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#8e44ad\">identity</text>\n            <text x=\"750\" y=\"540\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#8e44ad\">skip connection</text>\n            \n            <!-- Arrows for main path -->\n            <polygon points=\"460,740 455,730 465,730\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n            <line x1=\"460\" y1=\"740\" x2=\"460\" y2=\"710\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            \n            <polygon points=\"460,610 455,600 465,600\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n            <line x1=\"460\" y1=\"610\" x2=\"460\" y2=\"570\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            \n            <polygon points=\"460,470 455,460 465,460\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n            <line x1=\"460\" y1=\"470\" x2=\"460\" y2=\"430\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            \n            <polygon points=\"460,330 455,320 465,320\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n            <line x1=\"460\" y1=\"330\" x2=\"460\" y2=\"285\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            \n            <polygon points=\"460,220 455,210 465,210\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n            <line x1=\"460\" y1=\"220\" x2=\"460\" y2=\"150\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            \n            <polygon points=\"460,150 455,140 465,140\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n            <line x1=\"460\" y1=\"150\" x2=\"460\" y2=\"150\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Skip connection arrow -->\n            <polygon points=\"590,255 600,250 590,245\" fill=\"#9b59b6\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Bottleneck annotation -->\n            <rect x=\"50\" y=\"400\" width=\"200\" height=\"120\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#95a5a6\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n            <text x=\"150\" y=\"425\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Bottleneck Design</text>\n            <text x=\"150\" y=\"450\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#34495e\">256 \u2192 64 \u2192 64 \u2192 256</text>\n            <text x=\"150\" y=\"470\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#34495e\">Reduction ratio: 4\u00d7</text>\n            <text x=\"150\" y=\"490\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#34495e\">Params reduced by ~75%</text>\n            <text x=\"150\" y=\"510\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">Efficient computation</text>\n            \n            <!-- Legend -->\n            <rect x=\"1400\" y=\"200\" width=\"380\" height=\"500\" fill=\"#ffffff\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"1590\" y=\"230\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"18\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Legend</text>\n            \n            <!-- Legend items -->\n            <rect x=\"1420\" y=\"260\" width=\"40\" height=\"25\" fill=\"#fff2e6\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"3\"/>\n            <text x=\"1480\" y=\"278\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Convolution Layer</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"1420\" y=\"300\" width=\"40\" height=\"25\" fill=\"#f0f8e6\" stroke=\"#27ae60\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"3\"/>\n            <text x=\"1480\" y=\"318\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Batch Norm + ReLU</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"1420\" y=\"340\" width=\"40\" height=\"25\" fill=\"#e8f4fd\" stroke=\"#3498db\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"3\"/>\n            <text x=\"1480\" y=\"358\" font-size=\"12\" 